@startuml
title Whisper Mask Client – UML-Komponentendiagramm

skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam linetype ortho

actor "User" as User

component "Client Controller\n(run())" as Controller
component "Audio Input\n(PyAudio Microphone Stream)" as AudioInput
component "WebSocket Client\n(WebSocketApp)" as WSClient
component "AssemblyAI Streaming API" as AssemblyAI
component "Transcript Processor\n(Thread)" as TranscriptProcessor
component "DeepL Translation API" as DeepL
component "Speech Processor\n(Thread)" as SpeechProcessor
component "Google Cloud\nText-to-Speech" as GoogleTTS
component "Audio Player\n(Thread)" as AudioPlayer
component "MQTT Client" as MQTTClient
component "Mask Mouth Actuator\n(mask/mouth)" as Mask
component "WAV Recorder" as WAVRecorder

queue "transcript_queue" as TranscriptQueue
queue "text_to_speech_queue" as TTSQueue
queue "speak_queue" as SpeakQueue

database "Recorded Frames\n(recorded_frames)" as RecordedFrames
file "output.wav" as OutputWav
file "recorded_audio_<timestamp>.wav" as RecordedWav

User --> AudioInput : speaks into microphone

Controller --> AudioInput : initialize/open stream
Controller --> WSClient : create & start
Controller --> TranscriptProcessor : start thread
Controller --> SpeechProcessor : start thread
Controller --> AudioPlayer : start thread

AudioInput --> WSClient : audio chunks
WSClient --> AssemblyAI : stream audio
AssemblyAI --> WSClient : transcript messages / events

WSClient --> TranscriptQueue : enqueue formatted transcript
TranscriptProcessor --> TranscriptQueue : dequeue transcript
TranscriptProcessor --> DeepL : translate EN -> DE
DeepL --> TranscriptProcessor : translated text
TranscriptProcessor --> TTSQueue : enqueue translated text

SpeechProcessor --> TTSQueue : dequeue text
SpeechProcessor --> GoogleTTS : synthesize speech
GoogleTTS --> SpeechProcessor : audio_content
SpeechProcessor --> SpeakQueue : enqueue audio bytes

AudioPlayer --> SpeakQueue : dequeue audio
AudioPlayer --> OutputWav : write playback file
AudioPlayer --> MQTTClient : publish ON/OFF
MQTTClient --> Mask : control mouth animation
AudioPlayer --> AudioInput : <<independent>>
AudioPlayer --> OutputWav : playback via aplay

AudioInput --> RecordedFrames : append audio frames
RecordedFrames --> WAVRecorder : on session close
WAVRecorder --> RecordedWav : save session recording

WSClient --> WAVRecorder : trigger on_close()
WSClient --> Controller : error / close / terminate events

note right of WSClient
Handles callbacks:
- on_open()
- on_message()
- on_error()
- on_close()
end note

note bottom of TranscriptQueue
Thread-safe communication
between WebSocket callback
and transcript processor
end note

note bottom of TTSQueue
Thread-safe communication
between translation stage
and speech synthesis
end note

note bottom of SpeakQueue
Thread-safe communication
between TTS stage
and playback stage
end note

@enduml